          "discount": -0.25,
          "shipping_bonus": -1,
          "label": "Hostile \ud83d\ude24"
        }
      }
    },
    "rant_topics": [
      "the orbital cafeteria food situation",
      "his captain exam scores (near perfect)",
      "the injustice of the posting system",
      "deep space navigation theory",
      "the last supply ship crew who ignored him",
      "his meticulously maintained uniform",
      "the view from the relay window",
      "management bureaucracy",
      "the silence of space (he finds it peaceful)",
      "his detailed ship captain fantasy scenarios"
    ],
    "dialogue": {
      "greeting_neutral": [
        "Kovacs. What do you need.",
        "MF-7 relay. Make it quick.",
        "Yes. Still here. What.",
        "Kovacs. I was in the middle of something."
      ],
      "greeting_happy": [
        "Kovacs here. Good timing actually.",
        "MF-7. I'll admit, things could be worse today.",
        "Relay MF-7. You caught me in a reasonable mood."
      ],
      "greeting_hostile": [
        "What. WHAT. I'm busy.",
        "MF-7. This better be important.",
        "Kovacs. Don't test me today."
      ],
      "after_ask_wellbeing": [
        "Fine. Cafeteria ran out of the decent coffee again. But fine.",
        "Surviving. The posting review board denied my transfer. Again. But fine.",
        "You know what, that's... actually a reasonable question. I'm managing."
      ],
      "after_compliment_grooming": [
        "...thank you. I do maintain standards out here. Someone has to.",
        "I appreciate that. It's not easy keeping a pressed uniform on a relay station.",
        "Finally. Someone notices. The last three operators never once acknowledged the effort."
      ],
      "after_captain_dream": [
        "Since you asked \u2014 I scored 97th percentile on the navigation exam. 97th. And they put me here. Answering calls from moon farmers.",
        "You want to know about that? Most people don't ask. I had a full deep-space posting lined up. Politics. That's all I'll say.",
        "It's fine. I've filed the appeals. All twelve of them. One will land eventually."
      ],
      "after_listen_rant": [
        "...anyway. That's enough of that. What do you actually need.",
        "I appreciate you letting me finish. Most operators just hang up.",
        "Right. Sorry. It builds up out here."
      ],
      "after_rush_order": [
        "A RUSH order. Do you have any idea what that does to my scheduling.",
        "Fine. FINE. But this goes in my log. And your pricing reflects my inconvenience.",
        "Rush processed. You're welcome. My mood does not thank you."
      ],
      "after_dismissive": [
        "Charming. I'll remember that next time you need a favor.",
        "Noted. Enjoy the markup.",
        "Right. Well. I'll just add that to the list."
      ],
      "after_share_news": [
        "Hm. That's actually mildly interesting. Carry on.",
        "I see. The moon farming life. Riveting.",
        "Sure. Yes. Thanks for the update on your vegetables."
      ],
      "ship_window_reminder": [
        "Pickup is Week {week}. Have your cargo ready or I'm leaving without it. I have a schedule.",
        "Reminder: ship window opens Week {week}. Don't come crying to me if your silos are empty. \u2014 Kovacs",
        "Week {week} pickup approaching. I'll be overhead at the scheduled time. Whether you're ready is your problem."
      ],
      "ship_confirmed": [
        "Cargo received. {volume}m\u00b3 logged. Star-Scrip transfer processing. Next window: Week {next_week}.",
        "Shipment away. {volume}m\u00b3. You'll see the scrip next cycle. Try to have more next time.",
        "Received. {volume}m\u00b3. Logged. Transferred. I've filed the manifest. You're welcome."
      ],
      "rush_ship_confirmed": [
        "Rush shipment processed. {volume}m\u00b3. The surcharge reflects my feelings about this. \u2014 Kovacs",
        "Done. Rush fee applied. I hope whatever was so urgent was worth it."
      ],
      "no_cargo": [
        "You called me up here with an empty manifest. I have noted this in my personal log.",
        "Nothing to ship. Wasted trip. I'm adjusting my opinion of you accordingly."
      ],
      "contract_turnin": [
        "Contract fulfilled. {crop} delivery confirmed \u2014 {amount} units. Bonus scrip transferred. The colony is mildly pleased.",
        "Logged. {crop} contract closed. Bonus paid. Don't spend it all on seeds."
      ],
      "buy_confirmed": [
        "Order placed. Delivery on next drop \u2014 Week {week}. Don't complain about the prices. I don't set them.",
        "Purchased. Arrives Week {week}. You're welcome."
      ]
    }
  },
